# Crux Design System

## Tech Stack (Non-negotiable)
- Next.js 14 App Router
- TypeScript (strict mode)
- Tailwind CSS v3
- Framer Motion v11
- Shadcn/ui as base components
- Lucide React for icons
- next/font with Geist (primary) + Geist Mono (code)

## Design Tokens (tailwind.config.ts)

```ts
colors: {
  background: {
    DEFAULT: '#09090B',   // near-black base
    secondary: '#111113', // card backgrounds
    tertiary: '#18181B',  // elevated surfaces
  },
  border: {
    DEFAULT: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.08)',
    active: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.16)',
  },
  accent: {
    purple: '#7C3AED',
    'purple-light': '#A78BFA',
    blue: '#3B82F6',
    'blue-light': '#93C5FD',
    glow: 'rgba(124,58,237,0.4)',
  },
  text: {
    primary: '#FAFAFA',
    secondary: '#A1A1AA',
    muted: '#52525B',
    inverse: '#09090B',
  },
  status: {
    running: '#22C55E',
    pending: '#F59E0B',
    error: '#EF4444',
    complete: '#6B7280',
  },
}
```

## Typography Scale
- Display: Geist 72px/80px, weight 700, tracking -0.04em
- H1: 56px/64px, weight 700, tracking -0.03em
- H2: 40px/48px, weight 600, tracking -0.02em
- H3: 28px/36px, weight 600
- Body L: 18px/28px, weight 400
- Body: 16px/24px, weight 400
- Small: 14px/20px
- XS: 12px/16px, weight 500 (labels, badges)

## Spacing System
Use 4px base grid. Sections: py-24 lg:py-32. Cards: p-6 lg:p-8.
Container: max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8.

## Component Patterns

### Glass Card
```tsx
<div className="rounded-2xl border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.03] 
backdrop-blur-sm p-6 hover:border-white/16 
transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/[0.05]">
```

### Gradient Text (Headlines)
```tsx
<span className="bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-white/90 to-white/60 
bg-clip-text text-transparent">
```

### Glow Button (Primary CTA)
```tsx
<button className="relative px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-violet-600 
text-white font-semibold text-base
hover:bg-violet-500 transition-all duration-200
shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(124,58,237,0.4)] 
hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(124,58,237,0.6)]
active:scale-95">
```

### Agent Status Badge
```tsx
<span className="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 
py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border 
border-emerald-500/20">
  <span className="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 
  animate-pulse" />
  Running
</span>
```

## Animation Presets (Framer Motion)
```ts
export const fadeUp = {
  initial: { opacity: 0, y: 24 },
  animate: { opacity: 1, y: 0 },
  transition: { duration: 0.5, ease: [0.22, 1, 0.36, 1] }
}

export const staggerContainer = {
  animate: { transition: { staggerChildren: 0.08 } }
}

export const scaleIn = {
  initial: { opacity: 0, scale: 0.95 },
  animate: { opacity: 1, scale: 1 },
  transition: { duration: 0.4, ease: [0.22, 1, 0.36, 1] }
}
```

## Layout Rules
- Always dark background — no white pages except auth modals
- Every section has subtle radial gradient behind it 
  `bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_80%_50%_at_50%_-20%,rgba(124,58,237,0.15),transparent)]`
- Borders are always rgba white, never hard colors
- No card box-shadows — use glow effects only on CTAs
- Mobile-first breakpoints: sm(640) md(768) lg(1024) xl(1280)
```

